com.datasift.dropwizard.kafka.util
Class Compression

java.lang.Object
  com.datasift.dropwizard.kafka.util.Compression

public class Compression
extends Object

A utility for parsing CompressionCodecs from a Configuration.

To create Compression instances, use parse(String) to parse an instance from a String.

This is provided to parse textual specifications of a CompressionCodec, for example in a Configuration.
